  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread chicken, shrimp, mussels, and squid onto skewers.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together coconut milk, fish sauce, lime juice, ginger, and sea salt.",
    "Brush the seafood skewers with the marinade and let it sit for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Grill the skewers for 8-10 minutes, or until the seafood is cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, heat a small saucepan over medium heat and add the fermented kimchi.",
    "Stir the kimchi constantly until it is slightly caramelized, about 5 minutes.",
    "Serve the seafood skewers with the spicy kimchi sauce and garnish with fresh cilantro.",
    "Let the dish rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Slice the skewers and serve immediately."
  ],
